cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

The paper proposes a framework for motion prediction for autonomous vehicles, which involves analyzing sensor data and understanding typical motion patterns of freeway traffic. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to classify vehicle maneuvers and predict trajectories, indicating that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper is focused on autonomous vehicles, which suggests that it may also belong to the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
